The paper focuses on software engineering practices (such as anti-patterns) and their impact on the energy efficiency of mobile apps, which falls under the scope of cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also involves analyzing and testing android apps, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) or cs.MA (Mobile Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the limited resources of mobile devices and the need to consider energy efficiency, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.OH (Other Computer Science).
